597
00:57:46,510 --> 00:57:48,450
Dal si moje telefónne číslo

598
00:57:49,180 --> 00:57:51,320
inému mužovi?

599
00:57:52,660 --> 00:57:56,190
Áno, dal som ho No Kyung Woovi.

600
00:57:56,790 --> 00:57:58,080
Prečo?

601
